quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  30,6,( yeh ) khuda ka wada ( hai ) khuda apne waday ke khilaaf nahi karta lekin aksar log nahi jantay
  30,7,yeh to duniya ki zahiri zindagi ko jantay hain. aur akhirat ( ki taraf ) se ghaafil hain
  30,8,kiya onhon ne apne dil mein ghhor nahikiya. ke khuda ne asmano aur zameen ko aur jo kuch un dono ke darmain hai unn ko hikmat se aur aik waqt muqarrar taq ke liye pedakiya hai. aur bohat se log apne perwar-digaar se milnay ke qaail hi nahi
  30,9,kiya unn logon ne malik mein sair nahi ki ( sair karte ) to dekh letay ke jo log unn se pehlay they un ka injaam kaisay howa. woh unn se zoro qowat mein kahin ziyada they aur onhon ne zameen ko joota aur is ko is se ziyada abadkiya tha jo onhon ne abadkiya. aur unn ke paas unn ke paighambar nishanain le kar atay rahay to khuda aisa nah tha ke unn par zulm karta. balkay wohi apne aap par zulm karte they
  30,10,phir jin logon ne buraiee ki unn ka injaam bhi bura howa is liye ke khuda ki aayton ko jutlatay aur unn ki hansi uratye rahay they
  30,11,khuda hi khalqat ko pehli baar peda karta hai wohi is ko phir peda kere ga phir tum usi ki taraf lout jao ge
  30,12,aur jis din qayamat barpaa hogi gunehgaar na umeed ho jaien ge
  30,13,aur un ke ( banaye hue ) sharikon mein se koi un ka safarishi nah hoga aur woh apne sharikon se نامعتقد ho jaien ge
  30,14,aur jis din qayamat barpaa hogi is roz woh allag allag firqay ho jaien ge
  30,15,to jo log imaan laaye aur amal naik karte rahay woh ( bahisht ke ) baagh mein khush haal hon ge
